transcripts.text: Which America will you leave your grandchildren?  An America whose borders are open to drugs and crime?  Or one whose borders are secure?  An America whose cities provide sanctuary for criminal, illegal aliens?  Or one that follows and enforces the rule of law?  An America that gives your job to a foreign worker so corporations can increase profits?  Or one that cares about hardworking Americans like you?  Which America will you choose?  Paid for by Federation for American Immigration Reform?
